                            </li>
                            <li class="list-group-item bg-light-mint border-green">
                                <i class="fa fa-check-circle text-green"></i> ✔ Comprobante de domicilio
                            </li>
                            <li class="list-group-item bg-light-mint border-green">
                                <i class="fa fa-check-circle text-green"></i> ✔ Fotos del lugar donde vivirá la mascota
                            </li>
                            <li class="list-group-item bg-light-mint border-green">
                                <i class="fa fa-check-circle text-green"></i> ✔ Plan de cuidado
                            </li>
                            <li class="list-group-item bg-light-mint border-green">
                                <i class="fa fa-check-circle text-green"></i> ✔ Compromiso de visitas de seguimiento
